title: A Main to A Lobby ZERO/POINT
description: A good ZERO/POINT to use early for A Main.

title: Mid Market to B Main ZERO/POINT
description: A good ZERO/POINT to stop a rush or get info of players entering B Main.

title: B Lane to B Main FRAG/MENT
description: This is a good FRAG/MENT to disable a Killjoy Ultimate in B Main and prevent a push.

title: A Garden to A Cat Walk ZERO/POINT
description: This is a good ZERO/POINT for A Cat Walk from A Garden.

title: A Heaven to A Default FRAG/MENT
description: This is a good FRAG/MENT for post plant on A Default or to stop a plant.

title: A Main to A Site ZERO/POINT + FLASH/DRIVE
description: A good ZERO/POINT and FLASH/DRIVE combo to suppress and blind enemies on A Site.

title: B Garage to B Green ZERO/POINT
description: A good ZERO/POINT to suppress enemies playing around B Green.

title: A Nest to A Generator FRAG/MENT
description: This is a good FRAG/MENT for A Generator from under A Nest to push opponents out of the corner or to kill them.

title: A Belt to A Site FLASH/DRIVE
description: This is a good FLASH/DRIVE for A Site from A Belt that blind enemies peeking allowing your team to push.

title: A Belt to A Site FRAG/MENT
description: This is a good FRAG/MENT for A Site from A Belt to delay a defuse and secure the round.

title: Mid Blue to Mid Boiler ZERO/POINT
description: This is a good ZERO/POINT to suppress enemies playing in B Kitchen or Mid Boiler.

title: B Green to B Default FRAG/MENT
description: This is a good FRAG/MENT for B Site post plant.

title: A Nest to Top A Site FRAG/MENT
description: This is a good FRAG/MENT for A Site.

title: A Nest to A Default FRAG/MENT
description: This is a good FRAG/MENT for the default plant spot on A Site.

title: A Site to A Belt ZERO/POINT
description: A good ZERO/POINT to use early in the round to suppress enemies pushing A Belt.

title: B Site to B Yellow ZERO/POINT
description: A good ZERO/POINT to prevent enemies from pushing up and gauging how close the enemies are.

title: A Site to A Nest FLASH/DRIVE
description: This is a good FLASH/DRIVE to peek A Nest from A Site or to delay a push and re-position.

title: A Site to A Nest ZERO/POINT
description: This is a good ZERO/POINT for A Nest from A Site to suppress your opponents.

title: B Site to B Default FRAG/MENT
description: This is a good FRAG/MENT for B Site to stop a plant.

title: B Main to B Site ZERO/POINT + FRAG/MENT
description: A good combo of ZERO/POINT and FRAG/MENT to suppress and push enemies out of the back of B Site.

title: Defender Spawn ZERO/POINT From B Back
description: This ZERO/POINT for Defender Spawn from B Back is almost impossible to destroy, and can give you and your teammates valuable information as you try to take control of / hold B Site.

title: Mid Bottom To Mid Nest ZERO/POINT
description: This ZERO/POINT lineup is primarily useful for gathering information on Mid Nest / suppressing a player oping there so that they can't use utility to get out of an unfavorable position.

title: Close Left B Back ZERO/POINT From B Main
description: This ZERO/POINT is useful for suppressing / checking the close left corner in Back B Site that you see as you push out of B Main.

title: B Site to B Main ZERO/POINT
description: A good ZERO/POINT to delay an early push and get info into B Main.

title: A Site to A Lobby ZERO/POINT
description: A good ZERO/POINT to suppress enemies and get info on enemy positions.

title: Mid Wood Doors to B Elbow ZERO/POINT
description: A good ZERO/POINT to get info on enemies playing around B Elbow.

title: Right A Pyramid Pop Flash For A Cave Choke Point
description: This is a great FLASH/DRIVE from behind the right A Pyramid to pop flash players as they push out of A Cave into A Site.

title: B Main Choke Point FRAG/MENT From Back B Site
description: Here's a simple, but effective FRAG/MENT lineup for the chokepoint that connects B Main to B Site.

title: A Hall Pop Flash From A Metal Doors
description: This is a great FLASH/DRIVE from the A Metal Doors to pop flash players peeking into A Hall.

title: Mid Wood Doors ZERO/POINT From Defender Spawn
description: This ZERO/POINT for the Mid Wood Doors from Defender Spawn lands is almost impossible for the enemy team to destroy, unless they have a teammate in A Hall.
